quotes.content: Life is what happens to you while you're busy making other plans.
quotes.author: John Lennon

quotes.content: To be fully alive, fully human, and completely awake is to be continually thrown out of the nest.
quotes.author: Pema Chödrön

quotes.content: Every artist dips his brush in his own soul, and paints his own nature into his pictures.
quotes.author: Henry Ward Beecher

quotes.content: Love is composed of a single soul inhabiting two bodies.
quotes.author: Aristotle
